A WEB BASED WORD PRESS SOLUTION
A Three tier acrchitecture

In this project i demonstrated the power of thjree tire architecture showing that there can be communication three servers all meant to do different things aon the same project but 
with an common objective  of making sure the wordpree website is displayed and the project did just that at the end of the project.
For this project i created one Aws Ec2_instances of Ubuntu version 20.04 
distribution with all the configurations for free tier set up and it was meant to house the databsae server. while i also created three  Redhart  Ec2 instance
while i named the three of them wwbi web 2 and web3 all aprtictioned
